<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The King's Protocol</title>
    <style>
        /* / - Trader Style */
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #111; color: #ddd; }
        h1 { color: #fff; border-bottom: 2px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        h2 { color: #f1c40f; margin-top: 30px; } /*  */
        
        .task-item { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #222; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .task-item:hover { background: #1a1a1a; }
        
        /*  */
        .checkbox { width: 20px; height: 20px; border: 2px solid #555; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .task-item.checked .checkbox { background: #27ae60; border-color: #27ae60; }
        .task-item.checked { color: #555; text-decoration: line-through; }
        .checkbox::after { content: ''; color: #fff; display: none; font-size: 14px; }
        .task-item.checked .checkbox::after { display: block; }

        /*  */
        .reset-btn { margin-top: 40px; width: 100%; padding: 15px; background: #c0392b; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; }
        .reset-btn:active { opacity: 0.8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1> The King's SOP</h1>
    <div id="app"></div>
    <button class="reset-btn" onclick="resetAll()">RESET PROTOCOL</button>

    <script>
        // ==========================================
        // CONFIG AREA -  Markdown 
        // ==========================================
        const markdownSource = `
##  Boxing Pre-Flight
- [ ]  ()
- [ ]  ()
- [ ]  (/)
- [ ]  1 ()
- [ ] 

##  Recovery
- [ ]  10
- [ ] 
- [ ]  (Mental Note)

##  Trading Setup
- [ ] 
- [ ]  3 
- [ ] 
        `;
        // ==========================================

        const app = document.getElementById('app');
        const storageKey = 'kings_protocol_v1';

        //  Markdown List
        function render() {
            const savedState = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(storageKey) || '{}');
            const lines = markdownSource.split('\n');
            let html = '';
            
            lines.forEach((line, index) => {
                line = line.trim();
                if (line.startsWith('## ')) {
                    html += `<h2>${line.replace('## ', '')}</h2>`;
                } else if (line.startsWith('- [ ] ')) {
                    const text = line.replace('- [ ] ', '');
                    const isChecked = savedState[index];
                    html += `
                        <div class="task-item ${isChecked ? 'checked' : ''}" onclick="toggle(${index})">
                            <div class="checkbox"></div>
                            <span>${text}</span>
                        </div>
                    `;
                }
            });
            app.innerHTML = html;
        }

        function toggle(index) {
            const savedState = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(storageKey) || '{}');
            savedState[index] = !savedState[index];
            localStorage.setItem(storageKey, JSON.stringify(savedState));
            render();
        }

        function resetAll() {
            if(confirm('Confirm Reset?')) {
                localStorage.removeItem(storageKey);
                render();
            }
        }

        // Init
        render();
    </script>
</body>
</html>

    • Design a flat data structure in Firestore to handle these mixed types (Tasks, Cards, Books) efficiently.
